[Civil No. 811.] THOMAS F. WILSON, on behalf of the Territory of Arizona, Appellant, v. GEORGE W. VICKERS et al., Appellees. APPEAL from the' District Court1 of the Third Judicial District in and for the County of Maricopa. Edward Kent, Judge. E. S. Ives, for Appellant. Robert E. Morrison, for Appellees. March 20, 1903.

Affirmed (Memorandum), 203 U. S. 581.

Dismissed.
